baseMetaData.author: Bhaskar Neupane
baseMetaData.description: Want not to be seen on the internet? Then this is the perfect script for that purpose. Additionally, you will help the TOR network to be more anonymous. It's a win win for both. This script provides a way of managing how your TOR proxy will work so that you can focus on what you want rather than looking at technical issues.
baseMetaData.title: TOR IP Changer
